Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.20,0:03:24.30,zh,,0,0,0,,－我不喜欢　－好，什么？\N{\ren}- I don't love that. - Okay, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.37,0:03:26.26,zh,,0,0,0,,那当然，因为你们没性生活\N{\ren}Of course you don't. Cause you guys aren't getting any.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.71,0:03:30.98,zh,,0,0,0,,其实我们最近非常性积极\N{\ren}Actually, your father and I have been very sexpositive lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.05,0:03:33.48,zh,,0,0,0,,王医师建议我们多多尝试\N{\ren}- Eww. - Dr. Wong suggested we experiment.
