Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:36.53,zh,,0,0,0,,－一起看色情片　－好恶\N{\ren}- Together. - Gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.60,0:03:37.99,zh,,0,0,0,,我不想从海里回来了\N{\ren}I might never come back from the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.07,0:03:39.49,zh,,0,0,0,,你得低调点，宝贝\N{\ren}You'll have to tone it down, babe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.57,0:03:41.54,zh,,0,0,0,,这些凡人承受不了\N{\ren}The squares can't handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.78,0:03:43.83,zh,,0,0,0,,你们的牙齿里都有自杀胶囊\N{\ren}There are suicide capsules in all of your teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:45.38,zh,,0,0,0,,可以用用，莫蒂\N{\ren}Do what you want with that. C'mon, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:46.51,zh,,0,0,0,,你负责处理酒\N{\ren}You're on booze duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.58,0:03:48.09,zh,,0,0,0,,好，宁波只喝高级货\N{\ren}Okay, Nimbus only drinks the good shit
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.17,0:03:50.68,zh,,0,0,0,,所以把这酒丢进去\N{\ren}so just toss this whale-ass ocean wine in here
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.76,0:03:52.14,zh,,0,0,0,,放个几世纪\N{\ren}and age it up a few centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.22,0:03:53.69,zh,,0,0,0,,在里面时间过得比较快吗？\N{\ren}So, time moves faster in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.76,0:03:54.90,zh,,0,0,0,,像纳尼亚一样吗？\N{\ren}Is it like a Narnia thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.97,0:03:57.49,zh,,0,0,0,,我不是信上帝的海狸，莫蒂\N{\ren}I'm not a beaver who believes in Jesus Christ, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.98,0:03:59.57,zh,,0,0,0,,但确实就像纳尼亚那样\N{\ren}But yeah, it's pretty much a Narnia thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.65,0:04:02.33,zh,,0,0,0,,－但洁西卡… －你只负责端酒\N{\ren}- Okay, but Jessica... - All you have to do is bring wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.40,0:04:04.46,zh,,0,0,0,,－我拜托过你什么吗？　－你…\N{\ren}- When do I ask you for anything? - When do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.53,0:04:06.67,zh,,0,0,0,,我好几年没完整上过一周的课了\N{\ren}I haven't been to a full week of school in years!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.74,0:04:08.30,zh,,0,0,0,,我什么都不会，这是为了什么？\N{\ren}I don't know shit! And for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.37,0:04:10.01,zh,,0,0,0,,你到底有多少敌人？\N{\ren}How many enemies do you have to have?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.08,0:04:11.30,zh,,0,0,0,,为何老爱起冲突？\N{\ren}Why is everything a fight with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.38,0:04:12.76,zh,,0,0,0,,你要早点看清\N{\ren}You might want to learn this early, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.84,0:04:14.56,zh,,0,0,0,,－人生充满了冲突 －跟宁波先生吗？\N{\ren}- Life is a fight. - With Mr. Nimbus?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.63,0:04:15.73,zh,,0,0,0,,你在笑我吗？\N{\ren}Are you makin' fun of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.89,0:04:18.40,zh,,0,0,0,,宁波先生是冷血下体杀手，莫蒂\N{\ren}Mr. Nimbus is an ice-cold dick killer, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.02,0:04:20.99,zh,,0,0,0,,我们走，那是他的魔法海洋号角\N{\ren}Okay, let's go. That's his magic ocean horn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.53,0:04:29.84,zh,,0,0,0,,他是宁波先生吗？\N{\ren}Is that Mr. Nimbus?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:31.30,zh,,0,0,0,,－宁波　－理查德\N{\ren}- Nimbus. - Richard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.46,0:04:32.68,zh,,0,0,0,,你气色真差\N{\ren}You look like ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:34.05,zh,,0,0,0,,速战速决吧\N{\ren}Let's get this over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.21,0:04:35.56,zh,,0,0,0,,抱歉，就是他吗？\N{\ren}I'm sorry. This is the guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.63,0:04:36.93,zh,,0,0,0,,－杰瑞　－等等，不\N{\ren}- Jerry... - Hold on. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.01,0:04:38.39,zh,,0,0,0,,你是上过星球的人\N{\ren}I've seen you fuck a planet
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.47,0:04:40.82,zh,,0,0,0,,竟然怕他？\N{\ren}and this is the guy you're afraid of?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.89,0:04:42.57,zh,,0,0,0,,我喜欢这个，瑞克\N{\ren}I like this one, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.64,0:04:44.57,zh,,0,0,0,,他很健全且狂野\N{\ren}He is unbroken. Untamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.65,0:04:47.16,zh,,0,0,0,,或许我们应该把牵绳拉紧一点\N{\ren}Perhaps he could use a firmer grip upon his leash.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.24,0:04:48.96,zh,,0,0,0,,好，够了，我要报警了\N{\ren}Okay, that's enough. I'm calling the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.03,0:04:50.12,zh,,0,0,0,,－没问题　－杰瑞\N{\ren}- Go ahead. - Jerry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.20,0:04:52.21,zh,,0,0,0,,－我真的会　－我能控制警察\N{\ren}- I will! - Good. I control them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.29,0:04:54.55,zh,,0,0,0,,－什么？　－能控制警察，杰瑞\N{\ren}- Excuse me? - He controls police, Jerry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.71,0:04:57.18,zh,,0,0,0,,对，我如果会相信就太蠢了\N{\ren}Right, that tracks. In Dumb World.
