Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.06,0:10:43.82,zh,,0,0,0,,但我马上就要去拿酒来了\N{\ren}But... But... But I'll go get that wine right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.90,0:10:45.95,zh,,0,0,0,,但你已经这样说过两次了吧？\N{\ren}But you said were going to get it, like, twice already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.02,0:10:48.33,zh,,0,0,0,,没错，我现在真的要去拿了\N{\ren}I was, and I'm getting it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.28,0:10:51.67,zh,,0,0,0,,天啊，是他\N{\ren}Holy shit, it's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:57.10,zh,,0,0,0,,真是的，你们要我怎样？\N{\ren}God damn it! What do you want me to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.17,0:10:58.47,zh,,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\ren}I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.35,0:11:04.03,zh,,0,0,0,,我们总算打败他了\N{\ren}We finally beat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.10,0:11:07.28,zh,,0,0,0,,但我们要保持警觉，世事难料\N{\ren}But let's always remain vigilant, because you never know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.57,0:11:08.78,zh,,0,0,0,,他或许还会再来\N{\ren}He might be back one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.23,0:11:12.38,zh,,0,0,0,,好，纳尼亚，来吧，放马过来\N{\ren}Okay, Narnia! Let's go. Let's fucking go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.91,0:11:15.46,zh,,0,0,0,,结束了，那男孩不会再来了\N{\ren}It is over. The boy is not coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.54,0:11:17.09,zh,,0,0,0,,他一定会的\N{\ren}He always comes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:21.43,zh,,0,0,0,,你害我们赔上了人生还有未来，只为了一个虚构故事\N{\ren}You have wasted our lives, our very futures, on a fantasy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.51,0:11:23.48,zh,,0,0,0,,－一个谎言　－我确实看到了\N{\ren}- A lie! - I know what I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.55,0:11:24.73,zh,,0,0,0,,你什么都没看到\N{\ren}You saw nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.81,0:11:26.82,zh,,0,0,0,,蠢孩子\N{\ren}You are a foolish boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.73,0:11:33.00,zh,,0,0,0,,勇于看见真相的人\N{\ren}Those called fools are the only ones
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.07,0:11:35.17,zh,,0,0,0,,才会被骂蠢\N{\ren}brave enough to see the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.03,0:11:57.46,zh,,0,0,0,,告诉我，父亲\N{\ren}Tell me, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.87,0:11:59.71,zh,,0,0,0,,我还很蠢吗？\N{\ren}Am I a fool now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.58,0:12:05.39,zh,,0,0,0,,我出生于这些石块的制造地\N{\ren}I was born in the pits that made these stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.46,0:12:08.52,zh,,0,0,0,,我花很久时间建造这座谎言圣殿\N{\ren}I lost my years building a temple to a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.64,0:12:10.73,zh,,0,0,0,,所以我就把说谎当成我的能力\N{\ren}So, I made lies my power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.02,0:12:13.32,zh,,0,0,0,,能力其实就是我们…\N{\ren}And what is power, but a lie we...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.40,0:12:15.66,zh,,0,0,0,,天啊，是真的…\N{\ren}Oh, shit, he's real!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.73,0:12:17.29,zh,,0,0,0,,是真的，我搞错了\N{\ren}He's real! I was wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.36,0:12:19.79,zh,,0,0,0,,大错特错，神是…\N{\ren}I was so wrong! God is re...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:40.79,zh,,0,0,0,,服务真棒，我会给很多小费\N{\ren}Wow. Impeccable service. Big tip.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.86,0:12:42.67,zh,,0,0,0,,我比较喜欢另一个\N{\ren}I liked your other one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:44.29,zh,,0,0,0,,他叫什么吗？凯尔吗？\N{\ren}What was his name? Kyle?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.37,0:12:45.46,zh,,0,0,0,,－什么？　－没事\N{\ren}- What? - Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.54,0:12:47.18,zh,,0,0,0,,我们可以快点签约吗？\N{\ren}Can we just sign this thing and go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.54,0:12:49.81,zh,,0,0,0,,－洁西卡，真抱歉　－没关系\N{\ren}- Jessica, I'm so sorry. - I mean, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.88,0:12:52.10,zh,,0,0,0,,你才离开几分钟而已\N{\ren}You were only gone like a couple minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.22,0:12:53.39,zh,,0,0,0,,莫蒂，你还好吗？\N{\ren}Morty, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.47,0:12:55.06,zh,,0,0,0,,抱歉，洁西卡\N{\ren}I'm... I'm sorry, Jessica.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.14,0:12:57.03,zh,,0,0,0,,我们每次都搞砸，对吧？\N{\ren}We just never seem to get it right, do we?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.18,0:12:58.70,zh,,0,0,0,,是啊，的确如此\N{\ren}No, I guess we don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.77,0:13:00.20,zh,,0,0,0,,但我很高兴你打电话给我\N{\ren}But I'm glad you called me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.36,0:13:01.91,zh,,0,0,0,,我们可以重来\N{\ren}Maybe we can start over
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.19,0:13:03.50,zh,,0,0,0,,这次别再搞砸了\N{\ren}get it right this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.57,0:13:05.29,zh,,0,0,0,,好，我也想这样\N{\ren}Yeah. I'd... I'd like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.16,0:13:08.46,zh,,0,0,0,,谢谢你拿酒来\N{\ren}Thanks for bringing the wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.54,0:13:09.76,zh,,0,0,0,,非常值得\N{\ren}Totally worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.21,0:13:11.55,zh,,0,0,0,,需要开瓶器吗？\N{\ren}Do we need an opener?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.63,0:13:12.93,zh,,0,0,0,,我去拿\N{\ren}Oh. I'll... I'll go get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.92,0:13:17.44,zh,,0,0,0,,我很喜欢签约\N{\ren}Mmm. I do so love to sign upon the dotted line.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.51,0:13:19.44,zh,,0,0,0,,－要签了吗？　－没错\N{\ren}- Shall we? - Jesus Christ, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:21.99,zh,,0,0,0,,你的证人是谁？我的证人是这只鱿鱼\N{\ren}And who is your witness? My witness is the squid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.06,0:13:23.91,zh,,0,0,0,,你很喜欢海洋世界主题，对吧？\N{\ren}Really proud of this SeaWorld theme, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.98,0:13:26.00,zh,,0,0,0,,快去找证人，别怪到我头上\N{\ren}Hey, just get a witness, man. Don't make this about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.07,0:13:29.96,zh,,0,0,0,,或许他没有值得托付生命的人\N{\ren}Or perhaps, Richard has no one with whom he can trust his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.04,0:13:32.13,zh,,0,0,0,,除了我以外，没有人真正了解他\N{\ren}Who truly knows him, save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.21,0:13:34.64,zh,,0,0,0,,好吧，我去找人，天啊\N{\ren}Fine! I'll get someone. Oh, my god.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.71,0:13:37.14,zh,,0,0,0,,莫蒂，过来，我需要你做件鸟事\N{\ren}Morty! C'mere. I need you for some bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.22,0:13:38.98,zh,,0,0,0,,瑞克，我达成你的每一项要求了\N{\ren}Look, Rick, I've done everything you've asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.05,0:13:40.78,zh,,0,0,0,,我能好好陪我女朋友吗？\N{\ren}Can I just have some time with my girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.85,0:13:41.94,zh,,0,0,0,,女朋友？\N{\ren}Your girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.02,0:13:43.15,zh,,0,0,0,,她不是…\N{\ren}I mean, she's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.23,0:13:46.28,zh,,0,0,0,,我们接吻了，但我想慢慢来\N{\ren}We kissed, but I'm just trying to take it slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.40,0:13:48.25,zh,,0,0,0,,不可以太操之过急，懂吗？\N{\ren}You gotta give these things time to breathe, y'know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.08,0:13:54.22,zh,,0,0,0,,你知道你的特别之处吗，亚当？\N{\ren}Do you know why you're special, Adam?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.29,0:13:56.14,zh,,0,0,0,,－因为我是旅行者？ －对\N{\ren}- Because I am The Traveler? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.42,0:13:58.43,zh,,0,0,0,,你会穿越那扇门\N{\ren}You will be the one to pass through the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.76,0:14:01.23,zh,,0,0,0,,你会终结我们的痛苦\N{\ren}You will be the one to end our pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.30,0:14:03.52,zh,,0,0,0,,那我的痛苦呢，妈？\N{\ren}But, Mother, what about my pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.60,0:14:05.90,zh,,0,0,0,,你的痛苦会解放我们\N{\ren}Your pain shall set us free.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.98,0:14:07.66,zh,,0,0,0,,该开始了\N{\ren}It is time to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.61,0:14:12.67,zh,,0,0,0,,再来\N{\ren}Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.45,0:14:15.67,zh,,0,0,0,,再来\N{\ren}Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.50,0:14:21.27,zh,,0,0,0,,－你还没准备好 －拜托，妈\N{\ren}- You are not ready. - Please, Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:23.27,zh,,0,0,0,,你以为他会放过你吗？\N{\ren}Do you think he will show you mercy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.34,0:14:24.90,zh,,0,0,0,,看他对我们做了什么？\N{\ren}Like he did to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.97,0:14:26.11,zh,,0,0,0,,再来\N{\ren}Again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.72,0:14:44.93,zh,,0,0,0,,有人需要什么吗？\N{\ren}Does anyone need anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.01,0:14:47.36,zh,,0,0,0,,－宁波要什么吗？ －天啊\N{\ren}- Does Nimbus need anything? - Holy shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.43,0:14:49.19,zh,,0,0,0,,别评断我们，我们夫妻要一起成长\N{\ren}Don't judge. We're growing as a couple!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.98,0:14:51.41,zh,,0,0,0,,怎么会这样？\N{\ren}Why is this happening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.48,0:14:52.70,zh,,0,0,0,,为了未来\N{\ren}For the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.86,0:14:58.38,zh,,0,0,0,,你竟然想暗杀宁波？\N{\ren}You dare assassinate Nimbus?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.45,0:15:00.96,zh,,0,0,0,,－抱歉，等等，他是谁？ －还没轮到你，老兄\N{\ren}- Sorry, wait. Who is that? - Get in line, pal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.92,0:15:08.19,zh,,0,0,0,,真是浪费\N{\ren}Such a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:09.56,zh,,0,0,0,,妈？\N{\ren}Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.94,0:15:15.07,zh,,0,0,0,,洁西卡\N{\ren}Jessica!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.69,0:15:18.79,zh,,0,0,0,,你就是非碰海不可\N{\ren}You just had to touch the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.49,0:15:21.38,zh,,0,0,0,,闭嘴，我没时间…\N{\ren}Shut up! There isn't time to...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.45,0:15:23.34,zh,,0,0,0,,全都搞砸了，被你搞砸了\N{\ren}It's all fucked, and you fucked it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.30,0:15:30.19,zh,,0,0,0,,你提早来了\N{\ren}- Huh? - You're early.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.30,0:15:31.90,zh,,0,0,0,,这里是哪里？\N{\ren}Wh... What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.97,0:15:34.69,zh,,0,0,0,,是终点也是起点\N{\ren}The end. But also, a beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.77,0:15:36.95,zh,,0,0,0,,－每个终点都是起点，对吧？ －后退\N{\ren}- Isn't every end a beginning? - Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.02,0:15:39.37,zh,,0,0,0,,别跟我说些日舞科幻鬼话\N{\ren}I don't want your stripped down, Sundance sci-fi bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.44,0:15:41.33,zh,,0,0,0,,－洁西卡在哪？　－洁西卡\N{\ren}- Where's Jessica? - Jessica.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.41,0:15:43.08,zh,,0,0,0,,那是她的名字，对吧？\N{\ren}That was her name, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.16,0:15:45.13,zh,,0,0,0,,谢了，莫蒂，我都忘记了\N{\ren}Thank you, Morty. I had forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:48.18,zh,,0,0,0,,对了，你可以\N{\ren}Oh, right. You'll be needing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.17,0:15:50.39,zh,,0,0,0,,用这个酿酒\N{\ren}For the wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.30,0:15:56.32,zh,,0,0,0,,天啊，我们骗到他了\N{\ren}Oh, shit, we got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.56,0:15:59.11,zh,,0,0,0,,你敢相信他被这些鬼话骗了吗？\N{\ren}Can you believe he bought that fuckin' tree bullshit?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.19,0:16:00.49,zh,,0,0,0,,我们骗到他了\N{\ren}We fuckin' got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.73,0:16:05.63,zh,,0,0,0,,非常好，想跟亚特兰提斯开战，就顺你意\N{\ren}Very well. If you seek war with Atlantis, you shall have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.70,0:16:07.42,zh,,0,0,0,,我之前上美人鱼时\N{\ren}Oh, I've already been to war with Atlantis
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.50,0:16:08.88,zh,,0,0,0,,就已经开战了\N{\ren}when I DDay'd that Mermaid Puss!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.96,0:16:11.64,zh,,0,0,0,,我就知道是你，准备离场车队\N{\ren}I knew that was you! Prepare my exit parade.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.17,0:16:14.68,zh,,0,0,0,,跟你爱的干燥陆地道别吧\N{\ren}Say goodbye to your precious dry land
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.76,0:16:16.90,zh,,0,0,0,,这里很快就会变湿，超级湿\N{\ren}for soon, it will be wet! Wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.97,0:16:18.98,zh,,0,0,0,,全球暖化已经弄湿陆地了，混蛋\N{\ren}Yeah, global warming is already doing that, asshole.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.06,0:16:21.66,zh,,0,0,0,,尽管来吧，让我们变得更湿一点\N{\ren}But sure, yeah, go for it. Make us slightly more wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.73,0:16:24.41,zh,,0,0,0,,－你把我当笑话？　－对，没错\N{\ren}- Am I a joke to you? - Yes, you are a fucking joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.49,0:16:26.41,zh,,0,0,0,,你烂透了，你一直都很烂\N{\ren}You fucking suck! You've always sucked!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.49,0:16:28.46,zh,,0,0,0,,知道我们为何好几年没打仗吗？\N{\ren}You know why we haven't fought in years?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.53,0:16:30.71,zh,,0,0,0,,因为你很可笑，我不需要你了\N{\ren}'Cause you're an embarrassment to me, and I don't need you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.79,0:16:32.59,zh,,0,0,0,,我不靠别人，都在跟\N{\ren}I don't need anybody. All I do is eat ass
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.67,0:16:34.72,zh,,0,0,0,,任天堂做爱，每一天\N{\ren}and 69 Nintendos, bro. Every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:36.77,zh,,0,0,0,,或许你会讨厌我，是因为只有我\N{\ren}Or maybe, you hate me because I am the only man
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.84,0:16:38.19,zh,,0,0,0,,知道你变得多惨\N{\ren}to see how far you have fallen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.30,0:16:40.86,zh,,0,0,0,,我曾经害怕你，尊敬你\N{\ren}I used to fear you. Respect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:44.87,zh,,0,0,0,,但我现在只会可怜你这可悲酒鬼\N{\ren}Now all that's left is pity for a sad, drunk shell of a man
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:47.41,zh,,0,0,0,,你不敢承认自己有多寂寞\N{\ren}too afraid to see how alone he truly is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:49.96,zh,,0,0,0,,如果戴安还活着，她会怎么…\N{\ren}If Diane were alive today, what would she think...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.03,0:16:52.51,zh,,0,0,0,,少跟我讲另一个时空的背景故事\N{\ren}Don't fucking establish canonical backstory with me, you Red Lob...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.50,0:16:55.01,zh,,0,0,0,,很好，你醒了\N{\ren}Oh, good. You're awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.08,0:16:56.89,zh,,0,0,0,,我只是拿了些酒，我都道歉了\N{\ren}I just took some wine! I said I was sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.96,0:16:58.85,zh,,0,0,0,,你们有什么毛病？\N{\ren}What the fuck is wrong with you people?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.92,0:17:00.90,zh,,0,0,0,,我已经思考这件事好几世纪了\N{\ren}I have been asking that for centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.97,0:17:03.94,zh,,0,0,0,,他们建造我是为了研究你，莫蒂\N{\ren}I was created to study you, Morty. To know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.02,0:17:07.32,zh,,0,0,0,,但我越仔细看，就越不认得自己\N{\ren}But the closer I looked, the more I do not recognize myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.40,0:17:09.12,zh,,0,0,0,,好，我其实没时间…\N{\ren}Uh, yeah, man, I really don't have time for...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.19,0:17:11.83,zh,,0,0,0,,如果没有你，我们会是什么人？\N{\ren}I have often wondered... who would we be without you, Morty?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.03,0:17:14.09,zh,,0,0,0,,我们除了恨意还有什么？\N{\ren}Are we anything beyond our hatred?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.16,0:17:17.30,zh,,0,0,0,,她来的时候，我以为她会是答案\N{\ren}And when she came, I thought she would be the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.62,0:17:19.72,zh,,0,0,0,,被冻结在时间内，永远沉睡着\N{\ren}Frozen in time. Forever asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.96,0:17:22.77,zh,,0,0,0,,我们不懂她的意义，就把她隐藏起来\N{\ren}We could not understand her purpose, so we hid her away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.84,0:17:24.61,zh,,0,0,0,,我们为什么都要隐藏…\N{\ren}Why do we always hide the truths we...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.68,0:17:26.53,zh,,0,0,0,,我不在乎，放了她\N{\ren}I don't give a shit, nerd! Let her go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:28.32,zh,,0,0,0,,我干吗复制生殖器？\N{\ren}Why did I clone myself genitals?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:29.78,zh,,0,0,0,,我不在乎，动作快\N{\ren}- Ow! Ooh! - I don't care, bitch! Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.86,0:17:31.74,zh,,0,0,0,,－混蛋　－我就是混蛋\N{\ren}- Asshole! - Yeah, I guess I am an asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.82,0:17:33.33,zh,,0,0,0,,有时候就得当混蛋\N{\ren}Y'know, sometimes, you gotta be an asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.45,0:17:36.13,zh,,0,0,0,,－这是我外公教我的　－好吧…\N{\ren}- My grandpa taught me that. - Okay, okay, okay, fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.08,0:17:40.51,zh,,0,0,0,,－莫蒂？　－洁西卡\N{\ren}- Morty? - Hey, Jessica.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:42.51,zh,,0,0,0,,天啊，你一定睡得很熟，对吧？\N{\ren}Wow. Must've been some nap, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.71,0:17:44.81,zh,,0,0,0,,我不知道该怎么称呼这些东西\N{\ren}Is that, ooze or... I'm not sure what to call it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.88,0:17:46.56,zh,,0,0,0,,看起来像分泌物\N{\ren}It looks like ooze.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.64,0:17:48.48,zh,,0,0,0,,好，我们之后再聊\N{\ren}Okay. We can catch up later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.36,0:17:56.62,zh,,0,0,0,,什么…\N{\ren}What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.70,0:17:59.84,zh,,0,0,0,,瑞克\N{\ren}Rick! Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.91,0:18:01.34,zh,,0,0,0,,－死龙虾 －瑞克\N{\ren}- ...obster motherfucker. - Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.41,0:18:02.80,zh,,0,0,0,,－管他的，我在干吗？　－救命\N{\ren}- Screw this. What am I even doing? - Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.88,0:18:04.72,zh,,0,0,0,,你要去哪？\N{\ren}Where are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.80,0:18:07.27,zh,,0,0,0,,快回来 我会把陆地变湿\N{\ren}Come back here. I'm going to make the land wet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.34,0:18:09.19,zh,,0,0,0,,我倒想亲眼瞧瞧\N{\ren}Y'know what, I'd love to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.26,0:18:10.73,zh,,0,0,0,,放马过来，你要做什么都好\N{\ren}Do it! God, do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.81,0:18:13.11,zh,,0,0,0,,但别再拿我当借口了\N{\ren}Just don't use me as an excuse anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.19,0:18:14.24,zh,,0,0,0,,瑞克\N{\ren}Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.69,0:18:17.04,zh,,0,0,0,,天啊，真火爆\N{\ren}Wow. That was intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:19.62,zh,,0,0,0,,－你压力很大吗？ －我们签了文件\N{\ren}- You look stressed. - We signed the paperwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.70,0:18:21.50,zh,,0,0,0,,－我得走了 －你们有我们的电话\N{\ren}- I must go. - Your people have our number!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:23.55,zh,,0,0,0,,那只海星不是说有礼物篮吗？\N{\ren}Your starfish mentioned some kind of basket?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.62,0:18:25.05,zh,,0,0,0,,－莫蒂，能不能别…　－停止…\N{\ren}- Jesus, Morty. - Stop! No, no! Not today!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:26.60,zh,,0,0,0,,你不能就…\N{\ren}Can't you go one day without...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.84,0:18:29.43,zh,,0,0,0,,－什么…　－我搞砸了，好吗？\N{\ren}- What the... - I fucked it up, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.51,0:18:31.35,zh,,0,0,0,,没关系，莫蒂，你就是这样\N{\ren}It's okay, Morty. That's what you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.43,0:18:33.78,zh,,0,0,0,,我来拯救一切，带你们回家\N{\ren}Now, lemme deus ex machina this shit and let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.23,0:18:37.41,zh,,0,0,0,,天啊，为何大家都变机械鸟了？\N{\ren}God, why does everyone go cyberpunk bird?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.48,0:18:38.83,zh,,0,0,0,,真无趣\N{\ren}So fuckin' hack.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.16,0:18:43.75,zh,,0,0,0,,天啊，还真酷\N{\ren}Oh, shit. Well, that's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.09,0:18:52.69,zh,,0,0,0,,好吧，我们好像有点完蛋了\N{\ren}Okay, we might be a little fucked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.85,0:18:58.70,zh,,0,0,0,,你以为我会让你死吗，理查德？\N{\ren}Did you think I would let you die alone, Richard?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.30,0:19:14.56,zh,,0,0,0,,我是宁波先生\N{\ren}I am Mr. Nimbus!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.77,0:19:22.74,zh,,0,0,0,,你还有时间看电影吗？\N{\ren}Wow. You still got time for that movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.82,0:19:24.83,zh,,0,0,0,,对，时间\N{\ren}Yes. Time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.28,0:19:28.04,zh,,0,0,0,,我有很多时间，无尽的时间\N{\ren}I had nothing but time. Endless time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.95,0:19:30.51,zh,,0,0,0,,一开始只有疯狂\N{\ren}At first, it was madness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.58,0:19:31.84,zh,,0,0,0,,然后是启示\N{\ren}Then, enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.04,0:19:33.47,zh,,0,0,0,,然后又是疯狂\N{\ren}Then madness again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.75,0:19:35.97,zh,,0,0,0,,但这或许是好事\N{\ren}But perhaps it was a gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.17,0:19:38.02,zh,,0,0,0,,我看到了时间的生命\N{\ren}I could see the life of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.18,0:19:42.78,zh,,0,0,0,,正当我见证着时间悲惨的那一面\N{\ren}And as I watched the life of time in all its fleeting, terrible light
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.85,0:19:44.95,zh,,0,0,0,,我陷入了沉思，我有活过吗？\N{\ren}I wondered, had I lived?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.11,0:19:47.24,zh,,0,0,0,,我只是其他人故事中的物件吗？\N{\ren}Was I just the object in another's story?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.32,0:19:50.00,zh,,0,0,0,,我就仅此而已？这点能改变吗？\N{\ren}Was that all I ever was? Could I be more?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.16,0:19:53.05,zh,,0,0,0,,我有非常多的时间，却没有答案\N{\ren}I had nothing but time, and still no answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.16,0:19:55.18,zh,,0,0,0,,没有意义的时间就像是监牢\N{\ren}Time without purpose is a prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.33,0:19:57.43,zh,,0,0,0,,我看到了永恒的思想\N{\ren}I have glimpsed into the mind of eternity
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:19:59.31,zh,,0,0,0,,或是神的思想\N{\ren}perhaps the mind of God
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.68,0:20:01.36,zh,,0,0,0,,但我只找到寂静\N{\ren}and found nothing but silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.06,0:20:04.90,zh,,0,0,0,,我们还是当朋友就好\N{\ren}I think we should just be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:07.49,zh,,0,0,0,,好，我能理解\N{\ren}Oh, yeah. I... I get that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.73,0:20:09.33,zh,,0,0,0,,我们错过了时机\N{\ren}Guess we missed our moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.40,0:20:11.54,zh,,0,0,0,,对，但我们都会\N{\ren}Yes. But there will be more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.87,0:20:13.13,zh,,0,0,0,,有其他时机\N{\ren}For both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.20,0:20:14.34,zh,,0,0,0,,再见了，莫蒂\N{\ren}Goodbye, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.83,0:20:17.43,zh,,0,0,0,,－嘿，你好吗？ －滚，我是时间之神\N{\ren}- Hey, how's it going? - fuck off! I'm a time god.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.04,0:20:20.14,zh,,0,0,0,,我又跟你一同作战了，理查德\N{\ren}Fighting by your side again, Richard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.21,0:20:21.81,zh,,0,0,0,,－感觉很…　－没错\N{\ren}- It was, uh... - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.88,0:20:23.40,zh,,0,0,0,,那就不用签条约了\N{\ren}Then there is no treaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.47,0:20:24.65,zh,,0,0,0,,我们停战\N{\ren}Because there is no war.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.72,0:20:27.32,zh,,0,0,0,,宁波，你人真好\N{\ren}Aw, Nimbus. That's... That's really chill of you, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.39,0:20:30.53,zh,,0,0,0,,理查德，你在成为我的宿敌之前\N{\ren}Richard, before you were my greatest enemy
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.61,0:20:32.54,zh,,0,0,0,,你是我唯一的朋友\N{\ren}you were my only friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.61,0:20:33.87,zh,,0,0,0,,－爷爷，我弄到贝壳了 －操\N{\ren}- Grandpa, I got the shell! - Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.95,0:20:36.38,zh,,0,0,0,,－听着，宁波　－王八蛋\N{\ren}- Okay, Nimbus, look... - You son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.45,0:20:37.92,zh,,0,0,0,,－叛徒 －拿武器来，莫蒂\N{\ren}- Betrayal! - My weapons, Morty!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.00,0:20:39.42,zh,,0,0,0,,－我用光了 －爷爷\N{\ren}- I used them all! - Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.50,0:20:40.68,zh,,0,0,0,,怎么办？\N{\ren}Wait, Grandpa, what do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.75,0:20:42.18,zh,,0,0,0,,－贝壳在我这里，我要吹吗？要吗？ －别\N{\ren}- I have the shell. Should I blow it? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.25,0:20:43.43,zh,,0,0,0,,我直接吹好了\N{\ren}Is that... I'm just gonna blow it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.51,0:20:46.10,zh,,0,0,0,,－不要吹，砸烂它 －搞什么？\N{\ren}- Don't blow it! Destroy the horn! - What the hell, Summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.18,0:20:47.77,zh,,0,0,0,,要把贝壳砸烂\N{\ren}You were supposed to destroy the horn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.89,0:20:49.49,zh,,0,0,0,,我怎么会知道？\N{\ren}How was I supposed to know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.77,0:20:55.71,zh,,0,0,0,,警察，把这人渣关进牢里\N{\ren}Police! Take this piece of shit to jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.78,0:20:57.88,zh,,0,0,0,,我说过了\N{\ren}I told... I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.95,0:20:59.84,zh,,0,0,0,,他是冷血下体杀手\N{\ren}He's an ice-cold dick killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.12,0:21:01.22,zh,,0,0,0,,宁波\N{\ren}Nimbus!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.04,0:21:03.34,zh,,0,0,0,,等等，他怎么…\N{\ren}Wait. So, how can he...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.42,0:21:05.52,zh,,0,0,0,,天啊，桑美，他是宁波\N{\ren}Jesus, Summer. He's Mr. Nimbus.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.59,0:21:07.02,zh,,0,0,0,,他能控制警察\N{\ren}He controls the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.53,0:21:42.12,zh,,0,0,0,,杰瑞，太多安全语就失去意义了\N{\ren}Jer, I think more than one safe word sort of defeats the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.20,0:21:43.38,zh,,0,0,0,,我只是希望\N{\ren}I know, I just wanna make sure
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.45,0:21:45.17,zh,,0,0,0,,我们能有机会喊停\N{\ren}we have every opportunity to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.33,0:21:47.05,zh,,0,0,0,,但我很期待\N{\ren}Super excited about it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.12,0:21:48.55,zh,,0,0,0,,我也很期待\N{\ren}Me too, so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.34,0:21:51.81,zh,,0,0,0,,杰瑞，我们是真的想这么做吗？\N{\ren}Jerry, are we doing this because we both want this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.92,0:21:54.44,zh,,0,0,0,,还是我们以为对方想这么做？\N{\ren}Or because it's what we think the other one wants?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.68,0:21:56.40,zh,,0,0,0,,我只是想证明我很爱你\N{\ren}I just wanted to prove that I love you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.48,0:21:58.36,zh,,0,0,0,,－愿意为你做这种事 －我也是\N{\ren}- I would do this for you! - Same!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.44,0:22:01.03,zh,,0,0,0,,我们拿完奖品就走吧，不要犯下大错\N{\ren}Let's take that prize and get out before we make a huge mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.65,0:22:03.37,zh,,0,0,0,,后悔了？\N{\ren}Getting cold feet?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.95,0:22:06.29,zh,,0,0,0,,不，别告诉瑞克\N{\ren}No. Please don't tell Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.37,0:22:09.22,zh,,0,0,0,,－他不会懂的　－会，他会懂的\N{\ren}- He wouldn't understand. - Yes, he would.
